  "sectionIntros": {
    "lore": "",
    "timeline": "",
    "tree": "This is my section for family trees. I owe a great deal to the twilight wiki, twilight lexicon, and this one user on Reddit who connected all these family trees with painstaking effort (https://www.reddit.com/r/twilight/comments/mw2tr0/i_connected_all_the_quileute_family_trees_zoom_in/#lightbox). I've detailed the changes made to each family and why via notes! I hope you enjoy, these are canon for Dreaming!"
  },
